data.description: This incredible property in Bella Vista backs up to Sugar Creek, hole #4 on the Kingswood Golf Course, the OZ Trails ('Danger Will Robinson' trail), and is directly above the spectacular Sugar Bluffs Cave! The property has been well-maintained and offers generous rooms, including an all-season room right off the kitchen and living rooms. There are many space-use options for the large walk-out basement with a private full bathroom and extensive built-in cabinetry and shelving. Enjoy the beautiful views and all nature has to offer right in your backyard.
